enableColorScheme.description: Enable color-scheme CSS property to use theme.palette.mode. For more details, check out https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color-scheme For browser support, check out https://caniuse.com/?search=color-scheme
enableColorScheme.description_zh: 启用配色方案 CSS 属性以使用 theme.palette.mode。有关更多详细信息，请查看 https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color-scheme 有关浏览器支持，请查看 https://caniuse.com/?search=color-scheme
